Ultimate Aircraft (A Dorling Kindersley Book)
DK Publishing | 2000 | ISBN: 0789459612 | English | 184 pages | PDF | 36.3 MB

Ultimate aircraft - a celebration of the world's most exciting aircraft, from the Wright Flyer to the F-117 stealth fighter lavish large-format portraits of an unprecedented array of great flying machines evocative period photography and historic prints that capture the romance of aviation through the ages detailed profiles of the pioneers and innovators who transformed the way we travel and shaped history the ultimate guide for aficionados and novices alike
